**Instructions:** Think of church "experiences" you have worked on, supported, or participated in. Where might they have contributed to or amplified any of these distortions?

What design features can increase or combat distortion in our shared understanding?

How have I contributed to or been affected by the breakdown of shared understanding?  
What steps can I take to foster greater understanding in my digital interactions?

How can our church/Christian community better leverage technology to create shared understanding?  
What principles should guide our use of social media and other digital platforms?

**Activity Type:** discussion

**Group Size:** small-group

**Estimated Time:** 15-20 minutes